text: Oscar Bonini (born 13 July 1959) is an Argentine rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:Argentine male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Argentina Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
